# alp-python

Python reference implementation for ALP v1.

## Includes

- Pydantic protocol models
- JSON Schema validation
- Deterministic canonical JSON signing
- Ed25519 signing and verification
- Async HTTP client
- FastAPI receiver app
- SQLite-backed task store for local demo use

